OL,3,CMedics trial new detection scheme as
OL,4,Cheart failures predicted to rise
OL,6,FHospital has been chosen as one of
OL,7,Fseven across the British Isles to take
OL,8,Fpart in a pilot scheme designed to
OL,9,Freduce heart disease.
OL,11,FThe aim is to cut deaths by 25% in 25
OL,12,Fyears by using GP records to spot
OL,13,Ftriggers that could later lead to
OL,14,Fcardiological problems.
OL,16,FIt is estimated that between 1000 and
OL,17,F2000 people in Jersey are living with
OL,18,Fheart failure and that figure is
OL,19,Fexpected to rise over the coming years
OL,20,Fand decades.
