OL,6,FAaron Henry, Cardiology Fellow at
OL,7,Fadded: "Really sadly, we know that 4
OL,8,Fin 5 patients have their condition
OL,9,Fdiagnosed in hospital.
OL,11,F"Firstly it's about identifying those
OL,12,Fwho are at risk of heart failure and
OL,13,Fthen we will introduce them to the
OL,14,Fpreventative nurse, to prevent them
OL,15,Ffrom developing heart failure.
OL,17,F"It is not enough for our patients to
OL,18,Flive longer, we also want them to feel
OL,19,Fbetter during that time as well."
