OL,6,FTim Glennie was one of those
OL,7,Funknowingly living with heart failure.
OL,9,FHe said: "I was aware of some of the
OL,10,Fsymptoms if somebody had a heart
OL,11,Fattack but heart failure can be
OL,12,Fslightly different.
OL,14,F"I didn't associate shortness of
OL,15,Fbreath or the swelling of feet with
OL,16,Fheart disease and that's despite the
OL,17,Ffact that our doctors and nurses are
OL,18,Fboth friends and members of my
OL,19,Fextended family."
